Dealer's Choice is a cross-platform, networked multiplayer poker game
supporting draw, stud, and community-card variants, including Texas
Hold'em and Omaha, with optional wild cards. The deal rotates around the
table, and the dealer chooses the game before each hand.

Requires (all from SlackBuilds.org): canfigger, pcg-c, and protobuf-c.
canfigger homepage: https://github.com/andy5995/canfigger

Build options:
  TEST=yes   Run the test suite once during the build (via the One_pass
             meson setup) and save the results into the package's doc
             dir as test_results.txt. Default: no.
